#Compile and Run:

javac src/*.java
java src/SmartTrafficManagementSystem

# output

Every 10 seconds, the console will display the status of each traffic light as it changes.
After 30 seconds, the system will stop, and a message "Traffic management system stopped." will appear.


# Customization

Change Light Duration: Update the interval in TrafficController.start() from 10,000 milliseconds (10 seconds) to
a different value for longer or shorter light cycles.
